snippet.title: Nothing Good Can Come Of This -  Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A two-player local fighting game that strips combat down to its rawest form. Set in a bare room, players engage in intense fights over possession of a gun.

Now available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1096990/Nothing_Good_Can_Come_Of_This/

Music is Woochia - The Forbidden Door Pt.2, provided by Jamendo.
